@Forge.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7085

### Get all materials
GET {{Forge.Api_HostAddress}}/api/materials

### Create a material
POST {{Forge.Api_HostAddress}}/api/materials
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sku": "RM-001",
  "name": "Steel Sheet 2mm",
  "type": 0,
  "unitOfMeasure": "kg"
}

### Get material by id
GET {{Forge.Api_HostAddress}}/api/materials/1